{
  "text": "Genomic DNA was extracted from blood samples by standard methods. The coding sequence, cds, (10 exons) of BMPR1B was amplified by standard PCR protocols as reported previously. [CITATION_1] The cds of GDF5, NOG and IHH was also amplified and sequenced in a similar manner. Exact PCR conditions are reported elsewhere (for GDF5 12 ; for",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "25710410"
